---
title: Quick BBQ Chicken Schnitzel with Garden Salad & Sriracha Mayo
description: Who doesn’t love a good chicken schnitzel? Coated with a smokey BBQ-spiced crumb, paired with a refreshing garden
salad and a supercharged sriracha mayo, we bet this will be a real hit in the household tonight.

